import React from 'react';
import '../styles/logo.css'; // стили для анимации

function Logo() {
  return (
    <svg
      width="120"
      height="40"
      viewBox="0 0 120 40"
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      role="img"
      aria-label="Animated Logo"
    >
      <text
        x="10"
        y="30"
        className="logo-text"
        fontFamily="Arial, sans-serif"
        fontWeight="bold"
        fontSize="28"
        fill="#333"
      >
        MyGallery
      </text>
    </svg>
  );
}

export default Logo;
